1
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:42,000
Daughter,

2
00:01:42,720 --> 00:01:45,280
Heaven is sending you home.

3
00:01:45,320 --> 00:01:46,920
Daughter,

4
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:52,240
sending you home.

5
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:55,800
Daughter.

6
00:01:56,080 --> 00:01:58,400
Dad is sending you home.

7
00:01:58,440 --> 00:01:59,560
Master Lu,

8
00:02:00,520 --> 00:02:02,880
where are you going?

9
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:04,160
Our master has ordered

10
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:06,560
that you can't go anywhere.

11
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:09,120
Here.

12
00:02:09,160 --> 00:02:11,440
Daughter,

13
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:14,280
Dad is sending you home.

14
00:02:14,320 --> 00:02:16,320
Daughter.

15
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,320
Master Lu,

16
00:02:20,760 --> 00:02:22,720
where are you heading?

17
00:02:23,920 --> 00:02:26,680
My beloved daughter passed away from illness.

18
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:29,280
My younger sister is still missing.

19
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:33,480
I need to take her back to our hometown before the seventh day of her passing

20
00:02:33,480 --> 00:02:36,160
so she can rest in peace.

21
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:38,160
Lord Guan has ordered.

22
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:41,160
The Lu family is suspected of being involved in the disappearance of the Guan family's daughter.

23
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:43,520
Anyone entering or leaving the Lu residence must be inspected.

24
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:45,320
Please open the coffin,

25
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,560
so we can inspect it.

26
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:48,160
This...

27
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,720
How dare you!

28
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:51,680
The officers are here.

29
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:53,480
Is it your place to inspect?

30
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:56,440
The magistrate's office has been investigating this case.

31
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:57,900
Initial findings suggest

32
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:59,380
that my younger sister

33
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:00,920
has been murdered.

34
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:03,160
But we are still tracking down the suspect.

35
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:04,490
So we came to inform you.

36
00:03:05,640 --> 00:03:07,400
Thank you, thank you.

37
00:03:07,440 --> 00:03:09,440
Please find the real culprit quickly

38
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:12,200
to bring justice to the dead.

39
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:14,800
Since the Guan family cannot do it,

40
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:17,360
please inspect it, officers.

41
00:03:19,079 --> 00:03:20,079
No problem.

42
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:22,400
It is our duty to serve the people.

43
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:23,960
Then,

44
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,400
Jueming, go take a look.

45
00:03:31,760 --> 00:03:33,290
Excuse me, coming through.

46
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:15,840
Troupe Leader Lu.

47
00:04:19,079 --> 00:04:20,200
Coming.

48
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:22,120
Coming, coming.

49
00:04:23,400 --> 00:04:24,840
Butler. Troupe Leader Lu.

50
00:04:24,840 --> 00:04:26,360
What can I do for you?

51
00:04:26,640 --> 00:04:27,840
Troupe Leader Lu,

52
00:04:27,880 --> 00:04:29,320
there is good news.

53
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:30,720
What good news?

54
00:04:30,760 --> 00:04:34,560
The little girl you took in is the granddaughter of the Guan family.

55
00:04:36,159 --> 00:04:39,520
Master Guan specially sent me to take her home.

56
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:42,680
For this, we're giving you a cart of jewels

57
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:46,400
to thank you for raising her all these years.

58
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:49,960
From now on, you won't have to sleep in the open

59
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,480
and perform everywhere.

60
00:04:51,840 --> 00:04:53,680
No, Butler, it's like this.

61
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:56,120
This money is enough to last you a lifetime.

62
00:04:57,760 --> 00:05:01,320
We can't accept this.

63
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:11,960
Master.

64
00:05:14,880 --> 00:05:17,520
From now on, this is your home.

65
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:58,680
After all, she is just a woman.

66
00:05:58,760 --> 00:06:00,480
If it weren't for the death of my little grandson

67
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:01,940
and the family's decline,

68
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:04,850
I wouldn't have sought out outsiders.

69
00:06:05,440 --> 00:06:06,400
Master.

70
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:08,640
She was abandoned because the birthmark on her face

71
00:06:08,640 --> 00:06:10,900
would affect the Guan family's fortune.

72
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:14,240
Should we find a master to resolve it for her now?

73
00:06:14,280 --> 00:06:15,320
Of course.

74
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,480
Go do it now.

75
00:06:16,640 --> 00:06:17,480
Also,

76
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:18,920
arrange blind dates

77
00:06:19,440 --> 00:06:21,880
to find someone to marry into the Guan family as soon as possible.

78
00:06:21,880 --> 00:06:23,200
They need to have a chubby boy

79
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:24,720
to carry on the family line.

80
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:26,040
Yes.

81
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:41,000
Little sister, the Guan family sent someone to pick you up again.

82
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:42,480
They are right at the door.

83
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:44,200
I won't go.

84
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,760
Didn't you say at the time

85
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:49,760
that when you found me, you asked around and no one said they lost a child?

86
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:51,560
Master Guan seems to love me,

87
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:54,080
but he actually locks me in a cage like a bird,

88
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:55,560
makes me learn this and that,

89
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:57,000
won't let me see my brother and sister,

90
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,760
and won't let me do magic tricks.

91
00:06:58,760 --> 00:07:00,120
Yes.

92
00:07:00,840 --> 00:07:03,160
Oh, blame me for being slow-witted.

93
00:07:03,320 --> 00:07:05,440
When they asked about your background,

94
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:07,440
I sensed something.

95
00:07:07,760 --> 00:07:11,840
It seems the Guan family won't let this go easily.

96
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:13,120
When we found our little sister,

97
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:14,560
she was just a baby,

98
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:17,320
placed neatly in a corner.

99
00:07:17,960 --> 00:07:20,160
With the Guan family's power in Luoyang,

100
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:22,160
finding a lost child shouldn't be hard.

101
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,240
Is it hard?

102
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:26,000
Exactly, they are definitely up to no good.

103
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,040
Father,

104
00:07:34,440 --> 00:07:35,720
just say

105
00:07:36,520 --> 00:07:40,380
that my little sister wants to stay with me because I'm seriously ill.

106
00:07:42,720 --> 00:07:45,320
And she will return in a few days.

107
00:07:54,400 --> 00:07:58,040
We really can't bear to let our little sister return to the Guan family.

108
00:07:58,040 --> 00:08:00,560
So we will stall the Guan family first,

109
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:02,040
pack our bags,

110
00:08:02,080 --> 00:08:04,120
and prepare to go far away.

111
00:08:08,760 --> 00:08:10,080
Here you are.

112
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:13,640
Shh.

113
00:08:14,080 --> 00:08:15,360
There are people outside.

114
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:16,560
We can't leave.

115
00:08:16,960 --> 00:08:18,220
Then what should we do?

116
00:08:18,400 --> 00:08:19,720
What should we do?

117
00:08:19,760 --> 00:08:21,920
We can't really send Xiaomei back, can we?

118
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,680
No. Let's rush out.

119
00:08:30,400 --> 00:08:32,799
No. The courtyard is full of the Guans.

120
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,320
I have an idea.

121
00:08:35,559 --> 00:08:36,799
After I die,

122
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:39,600
cut off my limbs to make a decoy.

123
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,400
During the performance,

124
00:08:41,400 --> 00:08:43,080
Xiaomei will enter the wooden box,

125
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:45,600
and quickly replace it with the severed limbs,

126
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:48,680
letting all the audience witness this accident,

127
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:51,560
so they believe Xiaomei was kidnapped by robbers,

128
00:08:51,560 --> 00:08:54,520
and Xiaomei can escape in the chaos.

129
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:56,640
Your plan will absolutely not work.

130
00:08:56,640 --> 00:08:59,040
How can I let you die without an intact body?

131
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:01,170
I'm not leaving either.

132
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:06,320
Xiaomei, be a good girl.

133
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:10,880
Leave here with Father and Brother.

134
00:09:12,280 --> 00:09:13,280
No.

135
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:14,680
I want you to live.

136
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:16,360
I want you to be with me.

137
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:17,760
You are lying.

138
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:18,920
You lied to me.

139
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:20,360
You didn't keep your word.

140
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:22,520
Didn't we agree to go to Chang'an together?

141
00:09:22,520 --> 00:09:24,400
Pray at the temple together,

142
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:25,600
then get married together,

143
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:26,920
and have children together?

144
00:09:26,920 --> 00:09:29,920
We still have so many things to do. You lied to me.

145
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:34,800
Xiaomei.

146
00:09:35,280 --> 00:09:36,840
Because of this,

147
00:09:38,920 --> 00:09:41,120
you have to live a better life.

148
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:43,760
Get married for me.

149
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:45,840
Have children for me.

150
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:48,800
Perform on stage for me.

151
00:09:50,760 --> 00:09:51,840
Xiaomei.

152
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:54,040
Promise me.

153
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:58,000
Experience the world for me,

154
00:09:58,040 --> 00:09:59,440
okay? - No.

155
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,960
We are going together.

156
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:02,680
We promised each other.

157
00:10:08,560 --> 00:10:09,880
According to the plan,

158
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:12,040
cut off my limbs

159
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:14,120
to make a decoy

160
00:10:14,560 --> 00:10:16,160
and leave the Guan Manor.

161
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,280
No.

162
00:10:17,720 --> 00:10:18,960
Xiaomei,

163
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:21,160
listen to me.

164
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:27,400
When the Guan family finds out you have no limbs,

165
00:10:27,880 --> 00:10:30,440
Master Guan will definitely not pursue you anymore,

166
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:32,840
and he won't care about the troupe anymore.

167
00:10:37,880 --> 00:10:39,000
Xiaomei.

168
00:10:39,680 --> 00:10:41,400
You are naturally naughty

169
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:43,080
and like freedom.

170
00:10:43,160 --> 00:10:45,640
How can you stand a cage like the Guan Manor?

171
00:10:48,520 --> 00:10:50,520
Not just for me,

172
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:53,080
but also for yourself.

173
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:55,040
I can't promise you this.

174
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:58,560
We must be together. - I don't have much time left.

175
00:10:59,680 --> 00:11:02,080
Promise me this request,

176
00:11:02,160 --> 00:11:03,320
okay?

177
00:11:04,160 --> 00:11:06,800
Live well, okay?

178
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:11,440
Okay, I promise you, alright?

179
00:11:12,680 --> 00:11:14,320
I promise you.

180
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:17,600
Don't cry.

181
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:23,440
Don't leave me.

182
00:11:23,720 --> 00:11:25,160
Don't cry.

183
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:47,160
It has been confirmed

184
00:11:47,160 --> 00:11:48,890
that they are Lu Yue's remains.

185
00:11:50,680 --> 00:11:52,040
Daughter!

186
00:11:52,400 --> 00:11:55,440
My poor daughter!

187
00:11:59,400 --> 00:12:00,640
Master Lu.

188
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:02,560
My condolences.

189
00:12:02,640 --> 00:12:05,360
My condolences.

190
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:07,440
Master Lu,

191
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:10,680
if the young lady's remains are found,

192
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:12,480
and the Guan family refuses to take them,

193
00:12:12,480 --> 00:12:14,120
and you have not returned,

194
00:12:14,400 --> 00:12:16,120
where should she be buried?

195
00:12:18,040 --> 00:12:20,840
Under a pine tree at the foot of Dongpo Mountain.

196
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:23,400
Find a small plot to bury her.

197
00:12:23,520 --> 00:12:24,800
In front of the grave,

198
00:12:24,880 --> 00:12:28,000
just place a plum blossom branch.

199
00:12:30,520 --> 00:12:33,050
Your previous deduction was indeed correct.

200
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:35,520
When we found the last riddle

201
00:12:35,560 --> 00:12:36,960
and you told me

202
00:12:37,040 --> 00:12:39,640
the severed limbs were taken from the victims,

203
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:42,400
my earlier speculation was confirmed.

204
00:12:42,520 --> 00:12:45,000
What does that last riddle mean?

205
00:12:45,400 --> 00:12:48,200
Formless and shadowless, wandering everywhere,

206
00:12:48,280 --> 00:12:50,760
it sways willow branches in a gentle dance.

207
00:12:50,880 --> 00:12:53,160
It ripples the lake with a thousand waves,

208
00:12:53,160 --> 00:12:56,220
and wafts the scent of flowers over the small pavilion.

209
00:12:56,400 --> 00:12:58,080
The answer is the wind.

210
00:12:58,600 --> 00:13:00,320
The wind is free.

211
00:13:00,400 --> 00:13:02,880
How could it bear to be restrained?

212
00:13:06,040 --> 00:13:08,880
Little sister, look! The stars.

213
00:13:09,560 --> 00:13:12,360
Making a wish upon the stars is the most effective.

214
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:16,640
I hope before I leave,

215
00:13:17,280 --> 00:13:19,680
I can watch you perform one more time.

216
00:13:25,680 --> 00:13:28,080
Do you still remember our promise?

217
00:13:28,920 --> 00:13:30,960
We said we'd never part,

218
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:33,400
and always stay with the Lu Troupe.

219
00:13:35,920 --> 00:13:37,080
I remember.

220
00:13:37,400 --> 00:13:38,880
I said back then,

221
00:13:39,640 --> 00:13:41,120
'Silly girl,

222
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:45,240
in one year we'll have our coming-of-age ceremony.

223
00:13:45,400 --> 00:13:46,560
In the future,

224
00:13:47,040 --> 00:13:48,480
you'll get married

225
00:13:48,720 --> 00:13:50,160
and have children.

226
00:13:50,560 --> 00:13:53,560
How can you follow behind us for the rest of your life?'

227
00:13:54,080 --> 00:13:55,240
And I said,

228
00:13:56,280 --> 00:13:58,800
'I want to have my coming-of-age ceremony with you, Sister,

229
00:13:58,800 --> 00:13:59,800
get married together,

230
00:13:59,800 --> 00:14:01,200
and have children together.

231
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:03,280
Then I can always follow behind you.'

232
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:08,770
You are such a sweet talker.

233
00:14:09,800 --> 00:14:13,520
Do you remember where you said you wanted to go back then?

234
00:14:16,880 --> 00:14:18,080
I remember.

235
00:14:18,480 --> 00:14:19,880
I said

236
00:14:20,480 --> 00:14:24,800
I wanted to see the snow mountains of the Mohe tribe.

237
00:14:25,880 --> 00:14:29,000
I heard it's shrouded in snow and mist,

238
00:14:29,160 --> 00:14:30,480
with hanging ice waterfalls,

239
00:14:30,480 --> 00:14:32,000
and snow all year round.

240
00:14:33,440 --> 00:14:39,040
They say there's a silver crater lake at the top.

241
00:14:45,080 --> 00:14:47,340
I also wanted to go beyond the Great Wall,

242
00:14:47,920 --> 00:14:52,360
to experience the flying sand and endless rolling dunes.

243
00:14:53,600 --> 00:14:56,240
Or go to the picturesque

244
00:14:56,280 --> 00:14:59,880
Jiangnan water towns with their misty willows and painted bridges.

245
00:14:59,880 --> 00:15:01,240
In short,

246
00:15:02,040 --> 00:15:03,360
for me,

247
00:15:04,120 --> 00:15:05,600
what I long for

248
00:15:06,680 --> 00:15:10,520
is the vast world, the mountains, rivers, lakes, and seas.

249
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:12,040
This smoke is too heavy,

250
00:15:12,040 --> 00:15:13,640
it stings my eyes.

251
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:15,280
We made a pinky promise.

252
00:15:15,280 --> 00:15:16,400
Do you remember?

253
00:15:17,160 --> 00:15:19,680
You said we'd always be together,

254
00:15:19,840 --> 00:15:21,840
and you'd take me wherever you went.

255
00:15:30,920 --> 00:15:32,480
But little sister,

256
00:15:33,200 --> 00:15:35,160
I might not be able to go.

257
00:15:35,200 --> 00:15:36,920
You will go.

258
00:15:38,200 --> 00:15:40,200
You must promise me

259
00:15:40,800 --> 00:15:42,400
to live well,

260
00:15:42,600 --> 00:15:45,240
and visit those places for me.

261
00:15:47,040 --> 00:15:47,960
You can go.

262
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:49,600
We'll go together.

263
00:15:52,720 --> 00:15:53,840
I hope

264
00:15:55,120 --> 00:15:58,880
that in the future, you can be like the wind,

265
00:15:59,720 --> 00:16:01,360
blooming freely

266
00:16:02,240 --> 00:16:04,080
anywhere

267
00:16:04,480 --> 00:16:05,600
in the world.

268
00:16:05,640 --> 00:16:08,920
Sister, I will learn the magic tricks you taught me well.

269
00:16:08,960 --> 00:16:10,440
We'll perform together,

270
00:16:10,480 --> 00:16:12,040
see the world together,

271
00:16:12,080 --> 00:16:14,040
and bloom freely like the wind together,

272
00:16:14,040 --> 00:16:15,480
okay?

273
00:16:24,280 --> 00:16:26,840
Please don't leave me, okay?

274
00:16:32,360 --> 00:16:33,520
Little sister.

275
00:16:33,960 --> 00:16:35,720
You must remember me.

276
00:16:36,440 --> 00:16:38,920
But please don't cry anymore.

277
00:16:39,840 --> 00:16:42,400
Whenever you think of me from now on,

278
00:16:42,560 --> 00:16:44,400
you must smile.

279
00:16:48,920 --> 00:16:50,760
Sister.

280
00:17:06,880 --> 00:17:09,240
In front of the plum blossoms at the foot of Dongpo Mountain.

281
00:17:09,240 --> 00:17:10,480
This should be the place.

282
00:17:10,480 --> 00:17:11,440
Let's go.

283
00:17:14,440 --> 00:17:17,520
It seems Yueyue can finally rest in peace this time.

284
00:17:20,520 --> 00:17:23,720
So we rushed over just to let Boss Lu out of the city.

285
00:17:24,440 --> 00:17:25,960
But what about us?

286
00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:27,730
How are we going to report back?

287
00:17:27,960 --> 00:17:29,080
And what about your father?

288
00:17:29,080 --> 00:17:30,360
What should I tell him?

289
00:17:30,400 --> 00:17:32,880
The Guan family has too much power in Luoyang.

290
00:17:32,880 --> 00:17:34,560
We can't let them know.

291
00:17:34,640 --> 00:17:35,440
So,

292
00:17:35,480 --> 00:17:37,760
This secret stays between the three of us.

293
00:17:37,760 --> 00:17:39,320
You can't tell anyone else.

294
00:17:39,720 --> 00:17:41,360
As for my father,

295
00:17:41,400 --> 00:17:42,440
I'll figure something out.

296
00:17:42,440 --> 00:17:44,640
I won't put you in a difficult position.

297
00:17:44,840 --> 00:17:47,760
Our Coroner Li is now both kind and smart.

298
00:17:47,960 --> 00:17:50,760
And the ability to solve cases has also improved.

299
00:17:53,240 --> 00:17:54,440
Sometimes,

300
00:17:54,480 --> 00:17:57,080
not all cases must be solved.

301
00:17:59,600 --> 00:18:03,400
The three of us came to Yanzhi Alley in the North Market

302
00:18:03,440 --> 00:18:06,240
and found this last poetry riddle.

303
00:18:06,600 --> 00:18:08,760
After saying goodbye to Troupe Leader Lu,

304
00:18:08,760 --> 00:18:10,640
we followed the clues

305
00:18:10,680 --> 00:18:13,480
all the way to the outskirts.

306
00:18:13,640 --> 00:18:15,240
At this moment,

307
00:18:15,800 --> 00:18:18,440
the thief was riding away on a horse.

308
00:18:18,480 --> 00:18:20,920
We then drew our swords and left.

309
00:18:20,960 --> 00:18:22,800
How many thieves were there in total?

310
00:18:22,800 --> 00:18:24,440
Thir... thirty people.

311
00:18:27,520 --> 00:18:29,640
Thirty people.

312
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:31,440
Thirty people?

313
00:18:33,960 --> 00:18:35,960
Of course, thirty people.

314
00:18:36,520 --> 00:18:38,450
The Guan family is such a big prize,

315
00:18:38,520 --> 00:18:40,920
they were targeted by the thieves long ago.

316
00:18:41,680 --> 00:18:42,560
So,

317
00:18:42,880 --> 00:18:46,680
we tracked these thieves to the cliff.

318
00:18:49,400 --> 00:18:50,320
Mainly Su Lang.

319
00:18:50,360 --> 00:18:51,360
Su Lang

320
00:18:51,520 --> 00:18:52,920
took the frontline

321
00:18:53,160 --> 00:18:54,360
and fought ten at once.

322
00:18:54,360 --> 00:18:55,240
Swish, swish, swish, swish!

323
00:18:55,240 --> 00:18:58,720
He kicked them off the cliff one by one.

324
00:19:00,520 --> 00:19:01,880
Where is the body?

325
00:19:03,880 --> 00:19:07,240
There is a lake at the bottom of the cliff.

326
00:19:07,520 --> 00:19:09,280
It sank to the bottom.

327
00:19:09,400 --> 00:19:12,800
I mean our sister's remains.

328
00:19:13,400 --> 00:19:14,280
Our sister...

329
00:19:14,320 --> 00:19:17,040
She has already

330
00:19:17,440 --> 00:19:19,520
been chopped into many pieces.

331
00:19:19,600 --> 00:19:22,160
There is basically nothing left.

332
00:19:23,960 --> 00:19:24,720
I was thinking

333
00:19:24,720 --> 00:19:27,200
they probably dug a hole in the graveyard

334
00:19:27,240 --> 00:19:28,400
and buried her.

335
00:19:28,440 --> 00:19:29,760
That would be safe.

336
00:19:30,720 --> 00:19:31,480
Yes, yes.

337
00:19:32,880 --> 00:19:34,080
Brother Guan.

338
00:19:34,640 --> 00:19:37,560
Look, even though the suspect has been caught,

339
00:19:37,600 --> 00:19:41,640
the little granddaughter's remains haven't been fully found.

340
00:19:41,760 --> 00:19:42,600
Look at this.

341
00:19:43,560 --> 00:19:45,360
It's just one side of the story.

342
00:19:45,400 --> 00:19:47,400
There is no factual evidence at all.

343
00:19:47,440 --> 00:19:49,370
How can you expect me to believe it?

344
00:19:51,240 --> 00:19:52,520
You three,

345
00:19:52,800 --> 00:19:54,920
take some men to the graveyard immediately.

346
00:19:54,920 --> 00:19:56,760
Even if you have to dig three feet deep,

347
00:19:56,760 --> 00:20:00,360
you must find my little sister's remains for me.

348
00:20:00,880 --> 00:20:01,880
Yes, yes.

349
00:20:02,280 --> 00:20:05,120
Thank you for upholding justice for me, Deputy Governor.

350
00:20:05,120 --> 00:20:06,120
Brother Guan.

351
00:20:06,960 --> 00:20:08,320
Please don't thank me.

352
00:20:08,800 --> 00:20:10,880
It is my duty

353
00:20:11,040 --> 00:20:12,840
to protect the peace of this region

354
00:20:12,840 --> 00:20:15,400
and restore justice to the people.

355
00:20:16,120 --> 00:20:18,600
I will take my leave now.

356
00:20:18,680 --> 00:20:20,080
Take care, Brother Guan.

357
00:20:37,240 --> 00:20:39,280
Commissioner Li, where are you going?

358
00:20:39,280 --> 00:20:40,680
No need to ask.

359
00:20:41,240 --> 00:20:43,880
Send someone to search at once.

360
00:20:43,920 --> 00:20:45,080
Hurry up.

361
00:20:49,440 --> 00:20:50,560
What should we do?

362
00:20:50,640 --> 00:20:52,760
Take people to find her immediately.

363
00:20:52,800 --> 00:20:53,320
What should we do?

364
00:20:53,320 --> 00:20:55,560
Where should we look?

365
00:20:57,920 --> 00:20:58,800
Let's go.

366
00:21:00,000 --> 00:21:01,660
Then I don't need to go, right?

367
00:21:02,600 --> 00:21:05,240
Searching like this won't yield any results.

368
00:21:05,560 --> 00:21:07,600
Have you thought about how to wrap this up?

369
00:21:07,600 --> 00:21:09,400
This graveyard is so big.

370
00:21:10,320 --> 00:21:12,200
Maybe she was eaten by wild beasts.

371
00:21:12,200 --> 00:21:13,930
Just say that when you get back.

372
00:21:14,360 --> 00:21:15,040
I think,

373
00:21:15,080 --> 00:21:16,040
you should just say

374
00:21:16,040 --> 00:21:18,680
that Xiaomei fell into the lake with the bandit's bones.

375
00:21:18,680 --> 00:21:20,000
Wouldn't that be great?

376
00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:21,930
What if he asks you to fish them out?

377
00:21:22,120 --> 00:21:24,880
You'd be standing at the bow in the cold wind,

378
00:21:24,920 --> 00:21:26,560
directing everyone.

379
00:21:27,040 --> 00:21:29,170
In that case, the graveyard is better.

380
00:21:29,320 --> 00:21:30,480
But my father said,

381
00:21:30,520 --> 00:21:32,440
that there are many wronged souls buried in the eastern suburbs' woods.

382
00:21:32,440 --> 00:21:33,920
It's often haunted.

383
00:21:35,000 --> 00:21:37,120
When the Anlan Embankment collapsed back then,

384
00:21:37,120 --> 00:21:39,450
it caused a flood and drowned many people.

385
00:21:39,800 --> 00:21:40,960
Many of the deceased

386
00:21:41,000 --> 00:21:43,000
were residents of Luoyang City.

387
00:21:43,240 --> 00:21:44,520
In order to return to their roots,

388
00:21:44,520 --> 00:21:46,880
they brought the bones back to Luoyang.

389
00:21:47,320 --> 00:21:48,680
I heard that at night,

390
00:21:48,720 --> 00:21:50,560
you can hear people crying.

391
00:21:51,000 --> 00:21:51,960
Stop talking.

392
00:21:52,000 --> 00:21:53,200
He's scared.

393
00:21:53,240 --> 00:21:54,880
Then let's go back.

394
00:21:55,440 --> 00:21:56,560
Go back?

395
00:21:57,240 --> 00:21:58,160
Look around.

396
00:21:58,440 --> 00:21:59,840
With so many constables,

397
00:21:59,880 --> 00:22:02,200
do you think they're here to search the mountain?

398
00:22:02,200 --> 00:22:03,260
That's just an act.

399
00:22:03,280 --> 00:22:04,920
They're all here to keep an eye on me.

400
00:22:04,920 --> 00:22:05,960
Believe it or not,

401
00:22:06,200 --> 00:22:09,080
my father will interrogate them one by one tomorrow morning.

402
00:22:09,080 --> 00:22:10,520
If you're so afraid of your father,

403
00:22:10,520 --> 00:22:12,000
why are you a coroner?

404
00:22:12,160 --> 00:22:13,880
Being a coroner is my freedom.

405
00:22:13,920 --> 00:22:15,240
Do I look afraid of him?

406
00:22:16,880 --> 00:22:17,840
Are you okay?

407
00:22:18,000 --> 00:22:19,460
Did you get hurt anywhere?

408
00:22:19,920 --> 00:22:20,760
Get up.

409
00:22:22,200 --> 00:22:23,320
Are you hurt?

410
00:22:23,600 --> 00:22:24,560
I'm fine.

411
00:22:25,200 --> 00:22:25,840
Really?

412
00:22:25,880 --> 00:22:26,760
I'm fine.

413
00:22:26,960 --> 00:22:28,000
That's good.

414
00:22:28,040 --> 00:22:29,600
What could happen to me?

415
00:22:35,840 --> 00:22:37,280
Who is so inconsiderate

416
00:22:37,320 --> 00:22:38,720
as to leave a hoe here?

417
00:22:39,320 --> 00:22:41,840
Why is there a compass here?

418
00:22:43,880 --> 00:22:46,240
Constable Su, there are traces of grave robbers here.

419
00:22:46,240 --> 00:22:48,700
Constable Su, this side has also been dug up.

420
00:22:49,520 --> 00:22:51,050
And there's one over there.

421
00:23:01,520 --> 00:23:03,520
The soil is bright in color.

422
00:23:03,960 --> 00:23:07,690
It probably hasn't been exposed to the wind, sun, and rain for long.

423
00:23:08,080 --> 00:23:10,240
This group must have just left.

424
00:23:10,520 --> 00:23:11,920
Look, in this tomb,

425
00:23:11,960 --> 00:23:13,920
they dug up all the burial objects.

426
00:23:14,880 --> 00:23:16,920
And those untouched tombs

427
00:23:17,240 --> 00:23:18,240
show that

428
00:23:19,000 --> 00:23:21,360
they didn't have enough time to rob them.

429
00:23:21,440 --> 00:23:22,360
In my opinion,

430
00:23:23,800 --> 00:23:25,400
they will come back.

431
00:23:25,960 --> 00:23:28,360
Then let's lay an ambush right here

432
00:23:28,400 --> 00:23:30,120
and wait.

433
00:23:38,440 --> 00:23:41,760
We've been waiting for so long. Why is there no result?

434
00:23:43,200 --> 00:23:44,920
Why don't we go back?

435
00:23:46,960 --> 00:23:48,880
I think I know a place.

436
00:23:49,560 --> 00:23:50,680
The Ghost Market.

437
00:23:51,240 --> 00:23:52,520
Let's go ask.

438
00:23:52,560 --> 00:23:54,640
Maybe we'll get something.

439
00:24:10,360 --> 00:24:11,080
Follow me closely.

440
00:24:11,080 --> 00:24:12,160
Don't get lost.

441
00:24:19,040 --> 00:24:20,770
The Ghost Market is a mixed bag,

442
00:24:20,880 --> 00:24:22,940
gathering all sorts of street folks.

443
00:24:23,240 --> 00:24:24,360
It operates day and night,

444
00:24:24,360 --> 00:24:25,400
doing business as usual.

445
00:24:25,400 --> 00:24:26,320
New items.

446
00:24:27,040 --> 00:24:28,770
If you want to ask about anyone,

447
00:24:29,240 --> 00:24:31,520
or find lost items on the market,

448
00:24:31,800 --> 00:24:33,360
you can try here.

449
00:24:42,400 --> 00:24:43,360
Look here.

450
00:24:43,640 --> 00:24:44,920
This treasure gourd placed upside down

451
00:24:44,920 --> 00:24:47,640
means the shop has good stuff for sale.

452
00:24:47,720 --> 00:24:49,200
If it's placed upright,

453
00:24:49,240 --> 00:24:51,570
it means there's nothing good in the shop.

454
00:24:51,680 --> 00:24:53,760
Or the situation is relatively critical,

455
00:24:53,760 --> 00:24:55,000
and not suitable for trading.

456
00:24:55,000 --> 00:24:56,280
That's amazing.

457
00:24:56,840 --> 00:24:57,480
Let's go.

458
00:25:14,520 --> 00:25:15,520
No one's here.

459
00:25:19,840 --> 00:25:21,280
Do you want to find some items,

460
00:25:21,280 --> 00:25:23,440
or buy some treasures?

461
00:25:26,320 --> 00:25:27,280
Jueming,

462
00:25:27,680 --> 00:25:29,080
why are you here?

463
00:25:29,680 --> 00:25:31,140
Let me show you something.

464
00:25:31,840 --> 00:25:33,000
What is it?

465
00:25:34,440 --> 00:25:36,720
Take a good look at this for me.

466
00:25:37,000 --> 00:25:38,080
Whose is this?

467
00:25:42,720 --> 00:25:43,760
I don't know about this.

468
00:25:43,760 --> 00:25:45,200
This has nothing to do with me.

469
00:25:45,200 --> 00:25:47,680
No, stop messing around. Look closely.

470
00:25:47,840 --> 00:25:49,480
Take a good look.

471
00:25:49,560 --> 00:25:50,800
I am a constable of the yamen,

472
00:25:50,800 --> 00:25:51,760
handling a case on orders.

473
00:25:51,760 --> 00:25:53,690
How dare you conceal what you know?

474
00:25:54,320 --> 00:25:55,920
Looking at your clothes,

475
00:25:55,960 --> 00:25:58,000
I knew you were an officer.

476
00:25:58,320 --> 00:25:59,200
But here,

477
00:25:59,240 --> 00:26:00,160
it's the ghost market.

478
00:26:00,160 --> 00:26:02,280
The ghost market has its own rules.

479
00:26:02,320 --> 00:26:04,520
Don't talk about things you shouldn't.

480
00:26:04,520 --> 00:26:05,360
Here,

481
00:26:05,400 --> 00:26:07,160
you can't arrest me.

482
00:26:07,200 --> 00:26:08,320
If I speak,

483
00:26:08,360 --> 00:26:09,120
tomorrow,

484
00:26:09,160 --> 00:26:11,200
I'll be thrown into the river.

485
00:26:11,440 --> 00:26:13,360
- Then I'll take you back to the yamen and see if you confess.
- No, no, no, no.

486
00:26:13,360 --> 00:26:14,480
Su Lang.

487
00:26:20,000 --> 00:26:21,160
Indeed,

488
00:26:21,200 --> 00:26:24,280
we must follow the rules of the ghost market.

489
00:26:24,320 --> 00:26:25,560
- Right?
- Right, right, right, right.

490
00:26:25,560 --> 00:26:27,020
If you don't want to speak,

491
00:26:27,040 --> 00:26:28,280
you don't have to.

492
00:26:28,320 --> 00:26:29,880
I definitely won't force you.

493
00:26:29,880 --> 00:26:31,680
If you want to speak,

494
00:26:32,640 --> 00:26:34,440
It definitely has its benefits.

495
00:26:34,640 --> 00:26:36,360
This is really a good thing,

496
00:26:36,400 --> 00:26:39,040
but I'm still in a bit of a dilemma.

497
00:26:44,800 --> 00:26:46,720
How about now? Still in a dilemma?

498
00:26:48,040 --> 00:26:49,440
Not at all, not at all.

499
00:26:49,840 --> 00:26:50,720
I remember now.

500
00:26:50,760 --> 00:26:52,240
I remember everything.

501
00:26:52,560 --> 00:26:54,160
People who come here

502
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:56,160
never reveal their names.

503
00:26:56,440 --> 00:26:57,280
All I know

504
00:26:57,320 --> 00:26:59,520
is that these two are grave robbers.

505
00:26:59,560 --> 00:27:01,040
One is a man,

506
00:27:01,080 --> 00:27:01,880
not very tall,

507
00:27:01,920 --> 00:27:03,760
around his thirties,

508
00:27:03,800 --> 00:27:06,200
and he brought a thirteen or fourteen-year-old child.

509
00:27:06,200 --> 00:27:08,640
This child looks a bit foolish.

510
00:27:08,680 --> 00:27:09,880
His mind

511
00:27:09,920 --> 00:27:11,520
is quite unusual.

512
00:27:27,200 --> 00:27:28,600
It's you.

513
00:27:28,800 --> 00:27:31,360
What good stuff did you find this time?

514
00:27:31,520 --> 00:27:33,320
Got any more goodies?

515
00:27:35,520 --> 00:27:37,880
This time is different.

516
00:27:40,160 --> 00:27:42,760
I almost died in there trying to get this bead.

517
00:27:47,240 --> 00:27:48,080
Xiaobao,

518
00:27:48,560 --> 00:27:50,080
check if it's still alive.

519
00:27:56,080 --> 00:27:57,400
It's still alive.

520
00:27:57,600 --> 00:27:59,000
Then it's safe.

521
00:27:59,040 --> 00:28:00,170
Get ready to go down.

522
00:28:12,520 --> 00:28:13,880
To the honorable tomb owner,

523
00:28:13,880 --> 00:28:15,400
I am but a humble commoner.

524
00:28:15,440 --> 00:28:17,360
I have no other choice today,

525
00:28:17,400 --> 00:28:19,760
so I ask to borrow some of your treasures.

526
00:28:20,080 --> 00:28:21,840
If fate permits in the future,

527
00:28:21,880 --> 00:28:24,600
I will definitely return them in full.

528
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:50,600
Xiaobao, tug the rope once you find the treasure.

529
00:28:51,160 --> 00:28:52,080
Okay.

530
00:28:57,400 --> 00:28:58,320
Take it easy.

531
00:29:00,040 --> 00:29:00,960
Step firmly.

532
00:29:01,040 --> 00:29:02,040
Keep going down.

533
00:29:02,080 --> 00:29:03,040
You'll be fine.

534
00:29:09,920 --> 00:29:11,440
Where is the southeast corner?

535
00:29:11,440 --> 00:29:12,640
I don't know.

536
00:29:13,000 --> 00:29:15,330
Then I'll just put one in all four corners.

537
00:29:16,040 --> 00:29:17,520
I'm so smart.

538
00:29:22,880 --> 00:29:24,440
It's empty.

539
00:29:30,560 --> 00:29:31,800
There's a bead.

540
00:29:31,840 --> 00:29:33,040
Master said

541
00:29:33,080 --> 00:29:35,140
that beads are definitely valuable.

542
00:29:40,360 --> 00:29:41,760
This bead

543
00:29:41,920 --> 00:29:43,240
is worthless.

544
00:29:47,680 --> 00:29:50,160
The tomb you raided is empty.

545
00:29:50,600 --> 00:29:51,600
This means

546
00:29:51,640 --> 00:29:53,720
someone has definitely been there.

547
00:29:54,040 --> 00:29:56,500
How could they leave a precious bead for you?

548
00:29:57,320 --> 00:29:59,280
This is called a scent bead.

549
00:29:59,400 --> 00:30:02,120
It's carried around for its fragrance.

550
00:30:02,360 --> 00:30:03,560
It was most likely

551
00:30:03,640 --> 00:30:05,920
dropped by your fellow raiders.

552
00:30:09,400 --> 00:30:11,330
We've known each other for so long.

553
00:30:11,760 --> 00:30:12,880
You're not lying to me, are you?

554
00:30:12,880 --> 00:30:14,320
How could I lie to you?

555
00:30:14,360 --> 00:30:16,040
Look at what I do.

556
00:30:21,280 --> 00:30:22,800
Are there any other big tombs nearby?

557
00:30:22,800 --> 00:30:23,720
I don't know.

558
00:30:23,760 --> 00:30:25,000
I have no idea.

559
00:30:38,080 --> 00:30:39,280
It's yours.

560
00:30:39,360 --> 00:30:41,800
This thing is completely worthless.

561
00:30:44,680 --> 00:30:47,840
The bead is gone. Can we still eat meat?

562
00:30:47,920 --> 00:30:49,480
I'm hungry.

563
00:30:52,280 --> 00:30:54,920
Xiaobao, Master will take you to get some meat.

564
00:30:54,960 --> 00:30:56,640
Let's go. Okay.

565
00:30:59,200 --> 00:31:00,320
Fool.

566
00:31:07,200 --> 00:31:08,840
It's this bead.

567
00:31:08,880 --> 00:31:10,480
This is called Hexiang bead.

568
00:31:10,480 --> 00:31:11,410
It's worthless.

569
00:31:12,120 --> 00:31:14,120
It's used to enhance the fragrance.

570
00:31:16,120 --> 00:31:17,040
These two men,

571
00:31:17,080 --> 00:31:18,600
just fled here.

572
00:31:18,640 --> 00:31:20,040
If you want to catch them,

573
00:31:20,480 --> 00:31:22,320
they are short of money,

574
00:31:22,360 --> 00:31:24,490
so they will definitely strike again.

575
00:31:27,840 --> 00:31:28,640
Yesterday, this grave robber...

576
00:31:28,640 --> 00:31:29,520
Thank you. Here.

577
00:31:29,520 --> 00:31:32,120
Oh, you still have the nerve to eat and drink.

578
00:31:32,480 --> 00:31:34,240
I heard the dismemberment case of the Sun family's daughter

579
00:31:34,240 --> 00:31:35,720
hasn't been solved yet.

580
00:31:35,760 --> 00:31:36,640
Without me here,

581
00:31:36,640 --> 00:31:38,480
can't you solve a case?

582
00:31:39,720 --> 00:31:41,920
If I, Su Yu'an, were here,

583
00:31:41,960 --> 00:31:43,640
within two hours,

584
00:31:43,680 --> 00:31:45,680
I would definitely solve this case.

585
00:31:45,920 --> 00:31:47,360
I used to think

586
00:31:47,680 --> 00:31:50,040
we could analyze the case together.

587
00:31:50,080 --> 00:31:51,680
Everyone pitch in your ideas, okay? Thanks.

588
00:31:51,680 --> 00:31:52,880
We can still solve this case.

589
00:31:52,880 --> 00:31:54,120
But now I realize. Eat this, this.

590
00:31:54,120 --> 00:31:55,560
I'm the absolute core here.

591
00:31:55,560 --> 00:31:58,480
If I weren't here, you guys couldn't solve the case at all. Eat this.

592
00:31:58,480 --> 00:32:01,240
How about this? You guys brief me on the case,

593
00:32:01,280 --> 00:32:03,040
and I'll sort it out for you.

594
00:32:04,200 --> 00:32:06,330
What's going on with this case anyway?

595
00:32:09,240 --> 00:32:11,440
What exactly is happening with this case?

596
00:32:11,440 --> 00:32:12,560
Why so fierce?

597
00:32:12,600 --> 00:32:14,560
I'm just a lowly coroner.

598
00:32:14,600 --> 00:32:16,240
Let Constable Su explain it.

599
00:32:16,280 --> 00:32:18,520
Your dad is asking you. Jueming, you speak.

600
00:32:18,520 --> 00:32:19,480
You speak.

601
00:32:20,240 --> 00:32:21,360
I'll say it then.

602
00:32:21,400 --> 00:32:23,440
We were indeed investigating the Guan family's case,

603
00:32:23,440 --> 00:32:24,320
but that clue

604
00:32:24,360 --> 00:32:26,080
led us to the graveyard in the eastern suburbs.

605
00:32:26,080 --> 00:32:26,840
As soon as we went to check,

606
00:32:26,840 --> 00:32:28,800
wow, we found traces of tomb raiders.

607
00:32:28,800 --> 00:32:30,320
We staked out there all night,

608
00:32:30,320 --> 00:32:31,800
but found nothing.

609
00:32:31,880 --> 00:32:33,840
We plan to go back and stake out again after dinner.

610
00:32:33,840 --> 00:32:33,960
Yeah, yeah.

611
00:32:33,960 --> 00:32:34,560
Yeah.

612
00:32:35,160 --> 00:32:36,440
Did you go down into the tomb?

613
00:32:36,440 --> 00:32:37,100
Yeah, yeah.

614
00:32:39,040 --> 00:32:40,280
Come here. What is it?

615
00:32:42,320 --> 00:32:43,360
What is this?

616
00:32:45,360 --> 00:32:46,480
This piece of jade

617
00:32:46,640 --> 00:32:47,560
is natural.

618
00:32:47,600 --> 00:32:48,960
There are no carvings on it,

619
00:32:48,960 --> 00:32:52,360
so, playing on the homophone, it's called a 'Peace Pendant'.

620
00:32:52,560 --> 00:32:55,240
Wear it, and you'll be safe when going down to the tombs.

621
00:32:55,240 --> 00:32:56,080
It looks nice.

622
00:32:56,120 --> 00:32:57,000
Right?

623
00:32:57,040 --> 00:32:58,520
The pendant looks alright,

624
00:32:58,520 --> 00:33:00,240
but it doesn't seem to be worth much.

625
00:33:00,240 --> 00:33:01,520
Why are you so tactless?

626
00:33:01,520 --> 00:33:04,320
It doesn't even look as valuable as the treasure we found that day.

627
00:33:04,320 --> 00:33:06,120
Look how beautiful this bead is.

628
00:33:08,360 --> 00:33:09,440
Wait a minute.

629
00:33:13,240 --> 00:33:14,320
This bead

630
00:33:16,120 --> 00:33:18,200
must be the one given to me by Mrs. Qin.

631
00:33:18,440 --> 00:33:19,920
Which Mrs. Qin?

632
00:33:20,720 --> 00:33:22,160
Constable Qin's wife.

633
00:33:23,000 --> 00:33:24,520
Su Yuerong gave it to me.

634
00:33:24,560 --> 00:33:25,840
Su Yuerong?

635
00:33:26,520 --> 00:33:28,650
Then why would this bead be in the tomb?

636
00:33:28,800 --> 00:33:29,840
Right.

637
00:33:30,200 --> 00:33:31,660
How could it be? Back then,

638
00:33:32,240 --> 00:33:34,880
we had to enter a tomb to solve a case.

639
00:33:34,920 --> 00:33:38,360
So Constable Qin gave me this plain tablet,

640
00:33:38,400 --> 00:33:40,720
and Mrs. Qin gave me this incense bead.

641
00:33:40,760 --> 00:33:41,880
Enter a tomb?

642
00:33:42,280 --> 00:33:43,680
What case was he solving?

643
00:33:43,960 --> 00:33:46,560
The case of Junior Governor Cao's death.

